		"description": "<p><em>Breaker, Heavy, Two-Handed</em></p>\n<p>Large by even a giant&rsquo;s standards, this enormous hammer&rsquo;s handle is as long as a quarterstaff and its head is a simple log sharpened to a sturdy point. You gain a +2 magical bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this maul.</p>\n<p>In addition, while attuned this weapon has the following properties.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em><strong>Perceive Undead.</strong></em> You gain advantage on Perception checks made against undead and you are able to see undead that are invisible.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Powerful Attacks.</strong></em> You gain the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-feats.Item.e6506kodovstp5yw]{Powerful Attacker} feat, and while using the feat you gain advantage on attack rolls made against undead. If you already have the Powerful Attacker feat, instead your Strength score increases by 2.</p>",
